title: KILL Accenture and Huawei Help Guangdong CableTV Network Co. Ltd (GDCATV) Gain Efficiencies in Budget Planning and Support
text:
print this article - email to a friend - join our eNewsletter Submitted by admin on 9/17/2015 @ 9:06 PM 
-- (BUSINESS WIRE) -- Accenture requests that their press release NewsItemId: 20150917006284 entitled "Accenture and Huawei Help Guangdong CableTV Network Co. Ltd (GDCATV) Gain Efficiencies in Budget Planning and Support" be killed. 
The release issued by Accenture contains inaccurate information regarding Guangdong CableTV Network Co. Ltd. Please disregard this release, it will be reissued with correct information at a future date.
